---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="30 秒上手 — 塊頭勇者 Blockyusha" path="/devlog/how-to-play/" navActive="howto"
  description="塊頭勇者 30 秒上手教學：隊伍、屬性塊保存、CD技、combo、相剋一次看懂，還有核心循環動畫，看完就會玩。">

<div class="htp">
  <header class="htp-hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">How to Play</p>
    <h1>30 秒上手</h1>
    <p class="sub">拼方塊 × 卡牌 RPG — 看完就會玩</p>
  </header>

  <div class="htp-wrap">

    <div class="card lead">
      <p class="big">🧩 <b>一句話：</b>把方塊拼進 <b>9×9</b> 盤面，填滿一整<b>列／行／宮</b>就「消除」→ 對敵人造成傷害，消光敵人就過關。</p>
      <p class="muted">就像「<b style="color:var(--ink)">Woodoku 方塊消除</b>」，但每次消除都是在打怪。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="demo" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="demo-top">
        <div class="denemy" id="denemy">👹</div>
        <div class="dhp"><div class="dhp-fill" id="dhp"></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="dboard" id="dboard"></div>
      <div class="dcard"><span class="dslot" id="dslot"></span><span>屬塊存到卡上</span></div>
      <div class="dcap" id="dcap">拖方塊，填滿一個宮…</div>
    </div>

    <h2><span class="n">1</span>你的隊伍</h2>
    <div class="card">
      <p>一隊 <b>5 張勇者卡</b>，每張各「鎮守」盤面上的一個<b>宮（3×3）</b>，決定那個宮的<b>屬性</b>。</p>
      <p class="muted">盤面 = 9 個宮，對應你 5 張卡的屬性地圖。</p>
    </div>

    <h2><span class="n">2</span>招牌玩法：屬塊保存 ⭐</h2>
    <div class="card">
      <p class="big">這是本作最特別的地方 👇</p>
      <p>① 填滿一個<b>宮</b>消除時 → 那屬性會生成一塊「<b>屬性塊</b>」，<b>存到對應的勇者卡上</b>（卡上出現小方塊）。</p>
      <p>② 想用時，<b>從卡上把它「拖」到盤面</b> → 它是萬用塊，填任何空格、湊出更多消除（<b>連環爆發引擎</b>）。</p>
      <p>③ <b>不一定要馬上用！</b>可以一路囤 ——
        <b>前面小怪慢慢養塊，第 3 關 boss 一次狂放</b>，超有爽度。</p>
      <p class="muted">塊越大＝等級越高（清越多格生越大塊）。一張卡最高到 LV3；同屬疊兩張可衝 LV4～5。每張卡最多存 1 塊（留最高等的）。</p>
    </div>

    <h2><span class="n">3</span>五屬 & 形狀</h2>
    <div class="card" id="elements"></div>
    <div class="card">
      <p>🔥 火 / 🪨 土 / ⚡ 雷 的塊 <b>生成時就自動隨機轉好方向</b>（你不用手動轉，每次拿到不一樣）。</p>
      <p>💧 水 / 🌀 風 <b>方向固定</b>（直落 / 橫吹）→ 永遠知道會拿到什麼，最好規劃。</p>
    </div>

    <h2><span class="n">4</span>CD技（大招）</h2>
    <div class="card">
      <p class="muted" style="margin-top:0">每張卡<b style="color:var(--ink2)">上方有一顆小按鈕</b>，打幾手蓄滿後會發亮 → 點一下放招：</p>
      <div class="skill"><div class="ic">🔥</div><div class="tx"><b>業火奔流</b><div class="d">對全體敵人造成 攻擊×3 的爆擊</div></div></div>
      <div class="skill"><div class="ic">💧</div><div class="tx"><b>回春之泉</b><div class="d">回復 30% 生命</div></div></div>
      <div class="skill"><div class="ic">⚡</div><div class="tx"><b>封雷結界</b><div class="d">全體敵人延後 3 手才出手</div></div></div>
      <div class="skill"><div class="ic">🪨</div><div class="tx"><b>大地整復</b><div class="d">洗換手中的能量塊（換新一手）</div></div></div>
      <div class="skill"><div class="ic">🌀</div><div class="tx"><b>疾風亂舞</b><div class="d">combo直接衝到最高「極」</div></div></div>
    </div>

    <h2><span class="n">5</span>combo（連擊獎勵）</h2>
    <div class="card">
      <p>持續消除 → <b>combo</b>一階一階往上爬：<span class="muted">弱 → 中 → 強 → 超 → 極</span>。</p>
      <p>combo越高，<b>傷害倍率越大</b>（最高 ×1.8）；衝到「<b>極</b>」時攻擊會打<b>全體敵人</b>。</p>
      <p class="muted">一手清掉 2 組以上（暴擊）能直接把combo衝到頂。</p>
    </div>

    <h2><span class="n">6</span>相剋（帶對屬性更強）</h2>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="ring">
        <span class="e" style="background:var(--fire)">火</span><span class="ar">→</span>
        <span class="e" style="background:var(--wind)">風</span><span class="ar">→</span>
        <span class="e" style="background:var(--thunder)">雷</span><span class="ar">→</span>
        <span class="e" style="background:var(--earth)">土</span><span class="ar">→</span>
        <span class="e" style="background:var(--water)">水</span><span class="ar">→</span>
        <span class="e" style="background:var(--fire)">火</span>
      </div>
      <p style="text-align:center;margin-top:10px" class="muted">箭頭 = 剋。</p>
      <div class="pill">
        <span>剋到敵人 → 傷害 <b>×1.6</b></span>
        <span>被敵人剋 → 傷害 <b>×0.7</b></span>
      </div>
      <p class="muted">帶相剋的屬性去打對應關卡，會輕鬆很多 —— 但帶錯屬性只要操作夠好（衝combo、囤塊），一樣翻得回來。</p>
    </div>

    <h2><span class="n">7</span>卡住了？別怕</h2>
    <div class="card">
      <p>盤面塞滿、手上的塊放不下時 —— 只要卡上有<b>能用的屬塊</b>，它會<b>跳動發亮</b>提醒你，把它拖下去解圍，<b>不扣血</b>。</p>
      <p class="muted">真的連存的塊也救不了，才會花一點生命重洗。<b style="color:var(--ink2)">所以會玩的人幾乎不掉血。</b></p>
    </div>

    <h2><span class="n">8</span>一局心法</h2>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="flow">
        <div class="step"><div class="e">🌱</div><b>前期：養</b><div class="d">小怪關囤屬塊、衝combo</div></div>
        <div class="arrow">→</div>
        <div class="step"><div class="e">💥</div><b>Boss：放</b><div class="d">狂拖屬塊＋放大招爆發</div></div>
      </div>
      <p class="muted" style="margin-top:12px">盤面、combo、屬塊都會<b>帶到下一關</b>，所以一城 3 關是一場「連續戰」。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p class="muted">準備好了嗎？</p>
      <a class="btn" href="/play/">▶ 開始試玩</a>
      <p class="muted" style="margin-top:16px;font-size:12px;">塊頭勇者 · 開發中 Demo</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<style is:global>
.htp-hero{text-align:center;padding:34px 18px 8px}
.htp-hero h1{font-size:clamp(28px,7vw,40px);font-weight:900;letter-spacing:-.5px;margin:6px 0 4px;
  background:linear-gradient(120deg,#ff8a2a,#ff5a3d);-webkit-background-clip:text;background-clip:text;color:transparent}
.htp-hero .sub{margin:4px 0 0;color:var(--ink2);font-size:15px}
.htp-wrap{max-width:620px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 18px 70px}
.htp h2{font-size:19px;margin:36px 0 14px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;font-weight:900;color:var(--ink)}
.htp h2 .n{flex:none;width:30px;height:30px;border-radius:9px;color:#3a1f00;font-size:15px;font-weight:900;
  display:grid;place-items:center;background:linear-gradient(120deg,var(--cta1),var(--cta2));box-shadow:0 4px 10px rgba(255,140,40,.3)}
.htp .card{background:#fff;border:1px solid rgba(200,140,40,.18);border-radius:16px;padding:16px 16px;margin:10px 0;box-shadow:var(--shadow)}
.htp .card.lead{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#fff3cf,#fff8ec);border-color:rgba(255,178,32,.4)}
.htp p{margin:8px 0;font-size:15.5px;color:var(--ink)}
.htp .muted{color:var(--ink2);font-size:14px}
.htp b{color:var(--sun2)}
.htp .big{font-size:17px}
.htp .tag{display:inline-block;font-size:12.5px;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;background:rgba(255,178,32,.12);color:var(--ink2);margin-left:4px}
/* 屬性 */
.htp .elhead{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin:0 0 8px}
.htp .elhead .dot{width:30px;height:30px;border-radius:9px;display:grid;place-items:center;font-size:17px;flex:none}
.htp .elhead .nm{font-size:17px;font-weight:900}
.htp .elhead .ps{font-size:13px;color:var(--ink2);margin-left:auto;text-align:right;line-height:1.35}
.htp .shapes{display:flex;gap:9px;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:flex-end;margin-top:4px}
.htp .sh{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:4px}
.htp .sh .lv{font-size:11px;color:var(--ink2)}
.htp .grid{display:grid;gap:2px}
.htp .cell{width:11px;height:11px;border-radius:2px}
.htp .cell.on{box-shadow:inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,.15)}
.htp .cell.off{background:transparent}
/* CD技 */
.htp .skill{display:flex;gap:11px;align-items:flex-start;padding:9px 0;border-top:1px solid rgba(200,140,40,.16)}
.htp .skill:first-child{border-top:0}
.htp .skill .ic{width:34px;height:34px;border-radius:50%;background:#fff3cf;border:2px solid rgba(255,178,32,.4);
  display:grid;place-items:center;font-size:17px;flex:none}
.htp .skill .tx b{color:var(--ink)}
.htp .skill .tx .d{font-size:13.5px;color:var(--ink2)}
/* 相剋環 */
.htp .ring{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:6px;justify-content:center;font-size:14px;align-items:center}
.htp .ring .e{padding:3px 10px;border-radius:8px;font-weight:900;color:#fff}
.htp .ring .ar{color:var(--ink2)}
.htp .pill{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:8px}
.htp .pill span{font-size:13px;background:rgba(255,178,32,.1);border:1px solid rgba(200,140,40,.25);border-radius:8px;padding:3px 9px;color:var(--ink)}
.htp .footer{text-align:center;margin-top:40px;padding-top:22px;border-top:1px solid rgba(200,140,40,.18)}
.htp .btn{display:inline-block;margin-top:14px;font-weight:900;color:#3a1f00;font-size:16px;
  background:linear-gradient(120deg,var(--cta1),var(--cta2));padding:14px 34px;border-radius:999px;
  box-shadow:0 8px 0 #d96a00,0 14px 22px rgba(180,90,0,.3);transition:transform .12s,box-shadow .12s}
.htp .btn:active{transform:translateY(4px);box-shadow:0 4px 0 #d96a00,0 8px 14px rgba(180,90,0,.3)}
.htp .flow{display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:stretch;margin-top:6px}
.htp .flow .step{flex:1;background:#fff;border:1px solid rgba(200,140,40,.18);border-radius:12px;padding:12px;text-align:center;box-shadow:var(--shadow)}
.htp .flow .step .e{font-size:22px}
.htp .flow .step b{display:block;margin-top:3px}
.htp .flow .step .d{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--ink2)}
.htp .arrow{align-self:center;color:var(--sun2);font-size:20px;font-weight:900}
/* ===== 核心循環動畫 demo ===== */
.htp .demo{max-width:230px;margin:16px auto 2px;text-align:center}
.htp .demo-top{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:10px}
.htp .denemy{font-size:26px;line-height:1}
.htp .denemy.hit{animation:dshake .3s}
@keyframes dshake{0%,100%{transform:translateX(0)}25%{transform:translateX(-4px)}75%{transform:translateX(4px)}}
.htp .dhp{flex:0 0 96px;height:8px;background:rgba(0,0,0,.12);border-radius:99px;overflow:hidden}
.htp .dhp-fill{height:100%;width:100%;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#ff5a3d,#ff8a2a);border-radius:99px;transition:width .45s}
.htp .dboard{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:4px;width:126px;margin:0 auto;padding:6px;background:rgba(200,140,40,.1);border-radius:12px}
.htp .dboard .dc{aspect-ratio:1;border-radius:5px;background:rgba(200,140,40,.14);transition:background .15s}
.htp .dboard .dc.on{background:var(--fire)}
.htp .dboard.flash .dc.on{background:#fff;box-shadow:0 0 10px rgba(255,255,255,.9)}
.htp .dcard{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;margin-top:11px;font-size:12px;color:var(--ink2)}
.htp .dslot{width:16px;height:16px;border-radius:4px;border:1.5px dashed rgba(200,140,40,.55);display:inline-block;transition:.2s}
.htp .dslot.filled{background:var(--fire);border-style:solid;border-color:var(--fire);transform:scale(1.15)}
.htp .dcap{margin-top:11px;font-size:13px;font-weight:800;color:var(--sun2);min-height:18px}
[data-theme="dark"] .htp .dhp{background:rgba(255,255,255,.1)}
[data-theme="dark"] .htp .dboard{background:rgba(255,255,255,.05)}
[data-theme="dark"] .htp .dboard .dc{background:rgba(255,255,255,.07)}
[data-theme="dark"] .htp .dslot{border-color:rgba(255,178,32,.5)}
/* dark */
[data-theme="dark"] .htp .card{background:#231d14;border-color:rgba(255,178,32,.16)}
[data-theme="dark"] .htp .card.lead{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#2c2413,#231d14);border-color:rgba(255,178,32,.3)}
[data-theme="dark"] .htp .tag{background:rgba(255,255,255,.08);color:#e8d4a8}
[data-theme="dark"] .htp .skill{border-top-color:rgba(255,178,32,.14)}
[data-theme="dark"] .htp .skill .ic{background:#2b2014;border-color:rgba(255,178,32,.35)}
[data-theme="dark"] .htp .pill span{background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);border-color:rgba(255,178,32,.2)}
[data-theme="dark"] .htp .footer{border-top-color:rgba(255,178,32,.16)}
[data-theme="dark"] .htp .flow .step{background:#231d14;border-color:rgba(255,178,32,.16)}
[data-theme="dark"] .htp .cell.on{box-shadow:inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,.25)}
</style>

<script is:inline>
const SHAPES = {
  water:  {color:'#37b6ff', emoji:'💧', name:'水', ps:'直落 · 可靠好規劃', s:{1:[[0,0]],2:[[0,0],[1,0]],3:[[0,0],[1,0],[2,0]],4:[[0,0],[1,0],[2,0],[3,0]],5:[[0,0],[1,0],[2,0],[3,0],[4,0]]}},
  wind:   {color:'#3fbf54', emoji:'🌀', name:'風', ps:'橫吹 · 可靠好規劃', s:{1:[[0,0]],2:[[0,0],[0,1]],3:[[0,0],[0,1],[0,2]],4:[[0,0],[0,1],[0,2],[0,3]],5:[[0,0],[0,1],[0,2],[0,3],[0,4]]}},
  fire:   {color:'#ff6a3d', emoji:'🔥', name:'火', ps:'萬能可轉 · 每階都好用', s:{1:[[0,0]],2:[[0,0],[0,1]],3:[[0,0],[1,0],[1,1]],4:[[0,0],[0,1],[0,2],[1,1]],5:[[0,1],[1,0],[1,1],[1,2],[2,1]]}},
  earth:  {color:'#c8873f', emoji:'🪨', name:'土', ps:'方塊系 · 高手向，疊兩張超強', s:{1:[[0,0]],2:[[0,0],[1,1]],3:[[0,0],[1,1],[2,2]],4:[[0,0],[0,1],[1,0],[1,1]],5:[[0,0],[0,2],[1,0],[1,1],[1,2]]}},
  thunder:{color:'#f0b410', emoji:'⚡', name:'雷', ps:'鋸齒閃電 · 慢熱，LV3 後很猛', s:{1:[[0,0]],2:[[0,0],[1,1]],3:[[0,0],[1,0],[1,1]],4:[[0,1],[0,2],[1,0],[1,1]],5:[[0,0],[0,1],[1,1],[2,1],[2,2]]}},
};
function makeShape(cells,color){
  let mr=0,mc=0; cells.forEach(([r,c])=>{mr=Math.max(mr,r);mc=Math.max(mc,c);});
  const set=new Set(cells.map(p=>p[0]+'_'+p[1]));
  const g=document.createElement('div'); g.className='grid';
  g.style.gridTemplateColumns=`repeat(${mc+1},11px)`;
  for(let r=0;r<=mr;r++)for(let c=0;c<=mc;c++){
    const d=document.createElement('div');
    const on=set.has(r+'_'+c);
    d.className='cell '+(on?'on':'off');
    if(on)d.style.background=color;
    g.appendChild(d);
  }
  return g;
}
const host=document.getElementById('elements');
Object.values(SHAPES).forEach((el,i)=>{
  const block=document.createElement('div');
  if(i>0)block.style.cssText='border-top:1px solid rgba(200,140,40,.16);padding-top:13px;margin-top:13px;';
  const head=document.createElement('div'); head.className='elhead';
  head.innerHTML=`<div class="dot" style="background:${el.color}33;color:${el.color}">${el.emoji}</div>`+
    `<div class="nm" style="color:${el.color}">${el.name}</div><div class="ps">${el.ps}</div>`;
  block.appendChild(head);
  const row=document.createElement('div'); row.className='shapes';
  for(let lv=1;lv<=5;lv++){
    const sh=document.createElement('div'); sh.className='sh';
    sh.appendChild(makeShape(el.s[lv],el.color));
    const lab=document.createElement('div'); lab.className='lv'; lab.textContent='LV'+lv;
    sh.appendChild(lab);
    row.appendChild(sh);
  }
  block.appendChild(row);
  host.appendChild(block);
});

/* ===== 核心循環動畫 demo：填宮→消除→攻擊→存塊，循環 ===== */
(function(){
  var board=document.getElementById('dboard'); if(!board)return;
  var cells=[]; for(var i=0;i<9;i++){var c=document.createElement('div');c.className='dc';board.appendChild(c);cells.push(c);}
  var hp=document.getElementById('dhp'), enemy=document.getElementById('denemy'),
      slot=document.getElementById('dslot'), cap=document.getElementById('dcap');
  var order=[0,1,2,5,4,3,6,7,8], hpVal=100, timers=[];
  function T(fn,ms){timers.push(setTimeout(fn,ms));}
  function run(){
    timers.forEach(clearTimeout); timers=[];
    cells.forEach(function(c){c.className='dc';}); slot.className='dslot';
    cap.textContent='拖方塊，填滿一個宮…';
    order.forEach(function(idx,k){ T(function(){cells[idx].classList.add('on');}, 200+k*180); });
    var full=200+9*180;
    T(function(){ cap.textContent='整宮填滿 → 消除！'; board.classList.add('flash'); }, full);
    T(function(){
      board.classList.remove('flash');
      cells.forEach(function(c){c.className='dc';});
      cap.textContent='→ 對敵人造成傷害 💥';
      enemy.classList.add('hit'); T(function(){enemy.classList.remove('hit');},320);
      hpVal=Math.max(0,hpVal-34); hp.style.width=hpVal+'%';
    }, full+440);
    T(function(){ slot.classList.add('filled'); cap.textContent='屬塊存到卡上 ⭐（下次可拖出用）'; }, full+1000);
    T(function(){ if(hpVal<=0){hpVal=100;hp.style.width='100%';} run(); }, full+2500);
  }
  run();
})();
</script>
</Base>
